highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs Malaysia. “When Did You Get Hot?” is the highest at #32.
“Typing” by 樊宇镈(Coulson Fan) is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Malaysia, up 16 spots at #77.
“Let Down” by Radiohead has been on Viral Songs Malaysia the longest, at 109 days straight.
“Gata Only (Remix)” by FloyyMenor, Ozuna, and Anitta is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Malaysia at #94.
